aurynk (1.2.1) noble; urgency=medium
  Documentation improvements, packaging fixes, and enhanced developer experience.
  * New BUILDING.md: Comprehensive build guide for all platforms.
  * New TESTING.md: Complete testing guide with pytest, coverage, and debugging.
  * Enhanced CONTRIBUTING.md: Updated with modern structure and better guidelines.
  * Fixed Issue #62: aurynk_tray.py now follows proper Python packaging conventions.
  * Updated Snap packaging with proper USB device access (adb-support + udev).
  * Removed empty lib/ and tools/ folders from aurynk package.
  * Improved tray script installation across all packaging methods.
  * Better documentation structure with docs/ folder organization.

